1. This game is an open-world adventure game suitable for users aged 12 and above. It is recommended that minors use the game under the supervision of their guardians.

2. This game has main and side storylines, which are advanced through dialogue and interaction. The game also offers an open-world Explore gameplay. The game provides a small amount of text-based Stranger social system, and the management of this social system complies with relevant laws and regulations.

3. This game has a user real-name authentication system. Users who are authenticated as minors will receive the following game restrictions:
Users under the age of 8 cannot recharge; minors aged 8 and above but under 16, the single recharge amount shall not exceed 50 RMB, and the monthly recharge amount shall not exceed 200 RMB; minors aged 16 and above, the single recharge amount shall not exceed 100 RMB, and the monthly recharge amount shall not exceed 400 RMB.
Minors are not allowed to use the game from 22:00 to 8:00 the next day, and they are not allowed to use it for more than 3 hours on statutory holidays, and not more than 1.5 hours at other times.

4. The game unfolds the plot based on a fictional world, with distinctive art design, exquisite graphics, and high-quality game music.
